{"tid":1800170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台節目顧問團成員發起聯署冀增撥資源 逾5千人參與 (請Share)","createTime":"2019-12-27T14:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:36:37.000Z","uid":50294,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9780d60a126e0a8b0471c7abd8e4e5a56271dd19","tid":1800170,"uid":50294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>港台節目顧問團成員發起聯署冀增撥資源 逾5千人參與 (請Share)</strong><br />\n<br />\n27名香港電台節目顧問團成員發起聯署，致函商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，要求為港台增撥資源。公開信發出不足12小時，超過5500人加入聯署。商經局回應，港台作為政府部門一員，一直按政府資源分配機制獲得應有資源，提供公共廣播服務。港台有足夠資源，應付運作需要。<br />\n<br />\n商經局說，過去半年香港社會動盪，政府所有部門和各層級人員都要緊守崗位，克盡己職，多走一步，維持有效公共服務，又強調已多次指出，過去9年，港台開支累計增加超過一倍，高於同期政府經常開支累計增幅，公務員職位亦增加超過四成。<br />\n<br />\n港台節目顧問團的公開信指，港台新聞部因報道反修例運動花費大增，超出年度預算約500萬元，需要扣減人手，然而警隊過去半年逾時工作津貼開支共約9.5億元，待遇差天共地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499855-20191227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499855-20191227.htm&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3c835fff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499855-20191227.htm&h=91af4dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499855-20191227.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA%2Fviewform&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=a2c7394e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe0eZ9SHqpTj330WENMd-PGJDEcnnVNn9btktuFvrn0SG1-PA/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"6cea37af8f14f83b865c42cb42b2f771bd729a1a","tid":1800170,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bd0e9b0f5d036d0f63917280668b5b3483e1a3","tid":1800170,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"撐港台"},{"pid":"bf38bfea9c1b1aadac59862695482d75ff525a88","tid":1800170,"uid":50848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5beb17a48e6e841c870509e120fdad70dbb4514a","tid":1800170,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"港台真係高質<br />\n又係免費電視<br />\n屋企兩老都係睇佢"},{"pid":"845f550ded61017a791cbcf879f177b05b504ec3","tid":1800170,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"撐港台"},{"pid":"81ab1eb94b0735fbbb5d7a9af963f518b11b5022","tid":1800170,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}